file.name: config.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
    description: API access to your community.
    title: Vanilla API
    version: "2.0"
servers:
    - url: /api/v2
paths:
    /config:
        parameters:
            - name: test
              in: query
              description: Test parameter merging.
              style: form
              schema:
                  type: array
                  items:
                      type: string
components:
    schemas:
        Config:
            type: object
            properties:
                "perms.site.manage":
                    type: string
                    default: foo
                "perms.public":
                    type: integer
                    default: 1
                    x-read: public
                "perms.community.moderate":
                    type: boolean
                    default: true
                    x-read: member
                    x-write: community.manage
